name: Jennifer Moffett
text: Very friendly and helpful to out-of-towners. We will be back! We visited on June 12, 2021.

name: Jo-Amrah Dillingham
text: Great store! Wonderful unique merchandise. Friendly staff.

name: Kerry Bradford
text:
I’m new to town and this boutique was a great find. Very friendly and helpful staff plus
Regina (the owner) is a lovely lady. Lots of unique and special items to gift (or keep)!
Very happy I found this shop.

name: Alura Garrison
text: This place is so CUTE! What I love is that they carry many local artists. I got the most beautiful pieces of monogrammed pottery today.

name: CAROLYN STROMQUIST
text: Clerk was very helpful. Found a nice going away gift for a long time neighbor, who's moving to Maryland...Who, What, Where of Athens. Regina has an awesome selection of gifts. Rx

name: Jc
text: Great place to buy gifts for all the women in your life. Employees are very friendly and always helpful. Sells Claire Burke, jewelry, women's clothes, home decorations.

name: Charry Jones
text: Cute store and owner is super nice!

name: G Pierce
text: Very nice shop. Plan to return.
